text:
25/March/2025
Had dumpling soup ($5) for lunch, was normal. Nested inside a coffee shop. I'll be back to try their noodle next time round.
Decided to try it out having missed Soon Heng pork noodles that was previously in its place. Hits the spot, and would definitely come back again.

Not sure when this stall started after the previous one closed.
The 2 ladies serve a tasty bowl of bak chor mee soup. I tried the basic bak chor mee without add-ons.
